Module com.example.organizer
Package com.bookclub.mao

Class BookMAO

java.lang.Object
com.bookclub.mao.BookMAO
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.bookclub.iao.IBookAO
public class BookMAO extends Object implements com.bookclub.iao.IBookAO
This class is a mock implementation of the IBookAO interface, acting as a Mock Access Object (MAO) for performing operations related to Book objects. It stores a list of books and provides methods to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations.
